// ‚ö†Ô∏è  IMPORTANT: This code runs on the n8n SERVER, not in your browser!
// ‚ö†Ô∏è  Configure the timezone where you want executions to be scheduled,
//      regardless of where your n8n server is physically located.
//
// üìç Common timezone examples:
// - 'Europe/Paris'       ‚Üí Central European Time (CET/CEST)
// - 'America/New_York'   ‚Üí Eastern Time (EST/EDT)
// - 'America/Chicago'    ‚Üí Central Time (CST/CDT)
// - 'America/Los_Angeles'‚Üí Pacific Time (PST/PDT)
